From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Keyur Maru <kd2maru@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 11 Jul 2026 06:09:06 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] check_boot_jars: allow org.codeaurora.internal on the
 bootclasspath

telephony-ext (vendor/codeaurora/telephony) is a PRODUCT_BOOT_JAR providing the
org.codeaurora.internal.* IMS/telephony extension classes. AOSP's boot-jars package
check (run only by the full `m droid` target, not per-image builds) rejects it because
that package is not on the allow list, failing the build at platform-bootclasspath.
Allow-list it, matching how LineageOS carries telephony-ext.

Change-Id: I55e3177739d19daedb3ea3befe13adf2f3ba97b7
---
 scripts/check_boot_jars/package_allowed_list.txt | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/scripts/check_boot_jars/package_allowed_list.txt b/scripts/check_boot_jars/package_allowed_list.txt
index d13678f50927..0daa2a63befc 100644
--- a/scripts/check_boot_jars/package_allowed_list.txt
+++ b/scripts/check_boot_jars/package_allowed_list.txt
@@ -212,3 +212,9 @@ com\.google\.wear\..*
 # Packages used for display offload in Wear OS
 vendor\.google_clockwork\.displayoffload3
 vendor\.google_clockwork\.displayoffload3\..*
+
+###################################################
+# telephony-ext (CAF/LineageOS telephony extensions, a PRODUCT_BOOT_JAR on
+# vendor/codeaurora/telephony) — provides org.codeaurora.internal.*
+org\.codeaurora\.internal
+org\.codeaurora\.internal\..*
